title: Braun Series 9 electric shaver for men  -  Full video
description:
Watch the video to see the Braun Series 9 - our most efficient and advanced shaver.* 

The intelligent SyncroSonic technology delivers 40,000 cross-cutting actions per minute for an outstandingly thorough shave and amazing skin comfort. The Series 9 is the best shaver that combines ergonomic Braun Design with highest Braun quality. 

Braun - Designed to make a difference.

*Proven on 3 day beards.
